<p>
A <a href="/docs/Fields">field</a> implementing the Text <a href="/docs/Field_Types">field type</a> can store a string.
</p>

<p>
The Text <a href="/docs/Field_Types">field type</a> has two optional parameters named <code>Minimum Length</code> and <code>Maximum Length</code> that can be used to specify the acceptable lengths of the text.
</p>

<div class="heading">Example Field</div>
<pre>{
	"Name" : "My Text Field",
	"Field Type" : "Text",
	"Description" : "The example usage of the Text Field Type.",
	"Required" : true,
	"Parameters" : {
		"Minimum Length" : 3,//OPTIONAL
		"Maximum Length" : 140//OPTIONAL
	} 
}</pre>

<div class="heading">Example Value</div>
<pre>"ExampleUser.MyType.1" : {
	...
	"My Text Field" : "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.",
	...
}</pre>